Look, I guess what
I'm trying to say is...

237
01:05:49,420 --> 01:05:51,660
-We love you, Mr. Fronzi!

238
01:05:53,190 --> 01:05:55,590
-Mr. Jacob!
You mean it?

239
01:05:57,290 --> 01:06:00,890
Okay, guys,
we love you, Mr. Fronzi.

240
01:06:00,890 --> 01:06:02,860
We love you, Mr. Fronzi.

241
01:06:03,200 --> 01:06:04,730
We love you, Mr. Fronzi.

242
01:06:04,930 --> 01:06:06,570
We love you, Mr. Fronzi.

243
