remark, Lord Farrington.

261
02:00:35,230 --> 02:00:38,700
And I ask, sir, how dare you?

262
02:00:38,700 --> 02:00:40,870
-He asks him how he dares.

263
02:00:40,870 --> 02:00:44,770
