268
02:00:56,760 --> 02:00:59,360
I rebuke you, sir,

269
02:00:59,360 --> 02:01:00,690
and give it to you twice.

270
02:01:02,060 --> 02:01:03,700
-How dare you?

271
02:01:03,700 --> 02:01:06,800
