272
02:01:06,800 --> 02:01:08,000
-How dare you?

273
02:01:08,000 --> 02:01:09,640
How dare you?

274
02:01:09,640 --> 02:01:11,780
Ha! Dodge!

275
02:01:11,770 --> 02:01:13,100
-How dare you?!

276
02:01:15,740 --> 02:01:17,480
-How dare you?

277
02:01:17,480 --> 02:01:20,080
How to the absolute dare you?!

278
02:01:20,080 --> 02:01:21,220
-Gentlemen!

279
02:01:21,220 --> 02:01:23,320
You are beginning
to act like commoners.

280
02:01:24,320 --> 02:01:25,690
-How dare you?
-How dare you?

281
02:01:26,690 --> 02:01:27,860
How dare you?

282
02:01:27,860 --> 02:01:30,330
I am ungloved
and therefore unable to retort.

283
02:01:30,320 --> 02:01:33,290
Kedley, slap him as my proxy.
-Of course.

284
02:01:33,290 --> 02:01:34,860
-Mnh!
How dare you?

285
02:01:34,860 --> 02:01:36,760
-Very good.
-Gentlemen, stop!

286
02:01:36,760 --> 02:01:39,460
-We can't let this
silliness ruin the afternoon.

287
02:01:39,470 --> 02:01:41,610
Why don't you both
just apologize?

288
02:01:41,600 --> 02:01:43,130
-Apologize?

289
02:01:43,140 --> 02:01:46,010
I have done nothing wrong, sir.

290
02:01:46,010 --> 02:01:47,780
How dare you?

291
02:01:47,770 --> 02:01:48,770
-Don't do it.

292
02:01:48,780 --> 02:01:50,080
-I slapped you because --

293
02:01:50,080 --> 02:01:54,550
-Aah!
-Ohh!

294
02:01:54,550 --> 02:01:57,190
Ah, uh...

295
02:01:57,180 --> 02:01:59,480
Ho' 'are you?!

296
02:01:59,490 --> 02:02:00,860
How dare you?

297
02:02:00,850 --> 02:02:06,690
You struck me
with a closed fist!

298
02:02:06,690 --> 02:02:08,760
And, therefore,

299
02:02:08,760 --> 02:02:11,730
I am allowed to do the same.

300
02:02:11,730 --> 02:02:12,900
How dare you?

301
02:02:12,900 --> 02:02:14,670
-Enough!

302
02:02:14,670 --> 02:02:17,770
You, sir, have disobeyed
the Gentleman's Code.

303
02:02:17,770 --> 02:02:21,470
So I am permitted
to strike you with my cane.

304
02:02:21,470 --> 02:02:22,470
-Don't do it.

305
02:02:23,010 --> 02:02:24,380
-Oh, I'm so sorry.
Please don't hi--

306
02:02:27,080 --> 02:02:28,320
-Gentlemen!

307
02:02:28,310 --> 02:02:29,950
Stop this rabble at once.

308
02:02:29,950 --> 02:02:31,450
There are children present.

309
02:02:31,450 --> 02:02:32,750
Are you okay, sweetie?

310
02:02:32,750 --> 02:02:34,080
-How dare you?
-Oh, my God!

311
02:02:34,090 --> 02:02:35,790
-You strike a woman, boy?
How dare you.

312
02:02:37,820 --> 02:02:38,990
-Nice work.

313
02:02:38,990 --> 02:02:40,590
-This must cease.

314
02:02:40,590 --> 02:02:42,490
Look at this woman's dog.

315
02:02:42,500 --> 02:02:44,630
The commotion has frightened
the poor girl.

316
02:02:44,630 --> 02:02:48,600
Cede defeat, Farrington,
and end our quarrel now.

317
02:02:48,600 --> 02:02:50,300
-Ha ha!
Are you mad?

318
02:02:50,300 --> 02:02:52,100
Lord Pubert Farrington
would never bend his knee

319
02:02:52,100 --> 02:02:56,140
to appease
a frightened little...

320
02:02:56,140 --> 02:02:57,540
bitch.

321
02:02:59,150 --> 02:03:00,950
-How dare you?
-No!

322
02:03:00,950 --> 02:03:02,020
Skee-boop!

323
02:03:03,220 --> 02:03:04,960
-How dare --

324
02:03:04,950 --> 02:03:07,150
Yep, it seems
I've beshatted myself.

325
02:03:07,150 --> 02:03:09,250
Well, I cede defeat.
Well done.

326
02:03:09,260 --> 02:03:10,630
-Glad that's settled.

327
02:03:10,620 --> 02:03:12,660
Now, if you'll excuse me,
I'm off to retrieve my son,

328
02:03:12,660 --> 02:03:14,030
who I kicked across the park.

329
02:03:14,030 --> 02:03:15,700
-How dare you?

330
02:03:15,700 --> 02:03:18,100
I'm kidding. Good day.
-Good day.

331
03:00:03,400 --> 03:00:05,440
-Wow!

332
03:00:05,440 --> 03:00:07,940
First you take me to dinner
at Le Beef,

333
03:00:07,940 --> 03:00:11,110
and then you take me to the same
ice rink where we first met.

334
03:00:11,110 --> 03:00:13,710
I mean, this is the perfect
first-year anniversary.

335
03:00:13,710 --> 03:00:15,810
-And I haven't even
proposed yet.

336
03:00:16,850 --> 03:00:18,720
-Wait. What?

337
03:00:18,720 --> 03:00:22,290
-Candace Lorraine Dugan,

338
03:00:22,290 --> 03:00:23,960
