-Okay, that's going viral.

418
03:03:43,360 --> 03:03:45,190
-You guys are gonna be famous.

419
03:03:46,830 --> 03:03:48,230
-Tell me...

420
03:03:48,230 --> 03:03:49,730
Tell me what
you're thinking right now,

421
03:03:49,730 --> 03:03:50,900
and please be honest.

422
03:03:50,900 --> 03:03:53,740
-I mean, honestly,
I'm thinking...

423
03:03:53,730 --> 03:03:57,970
there's no way the Egyptian
thing goes viral, right?

424
03:03:57,970 --> 03:04:00,110
-Oh. Okay. Okay.
Goodbye, Casper.

425
03:04:00,110 --> 03:04:02,610
-Candace, wait.
Okay? You're right.

426
03:04:02,610 --> 03:04:04,410
I'm sorry.
I -- I have felt distracted,

427
03:04:04,410 --> 03:04:06,080
but we can work through it.

428
03:04:06,080 --> 03:04:09,180
-♪ Backwards, back, alright ♪

429
03:04:09,180 --> 03:04:11,680
-♪ Oh, my God,
we're backwards again ♪

430
03:04:11,690 --> 03:04:14,760
-You guys, slow down.
If I fall, Kendrick Lamar

431
03:04:14,750 --> 03:04:17,490
is literally gonna need to find
himself a new producer.

432
03:04:18,630 --> 03:04:21,200
-I don't understand.

433
03:04:21,190 --> 03:04:23,420
-Right?
Like, how is that guy

434
03:04:23,430 --> 03:04:26,800
in any way associated
with Kendrick Lamar?

435
03:04:26,800 --> 03:04:30,240
-I'm not talking
about those guys!

436
03:04:30,240 --> 03:04:32,340
You know what?

437
03:04:32,340 --> 03:04:34,310
Maybe this is a sign.

438
03:04:34,310 --> 03:04:38,250
Maybe what we both actually
need is some time apart.

439
03:04:38,250 --> 03:04:41,620
-Okay. Sounds good.
I'm gonna hang with these guys.

440
03:04:41,620 --> 03:04:43,360
I have to figure out
their secret.

441
03:04:43,350 --> 03:04:46,650
-Ha ha! Our secret?
One word.

442
03:04:46,650 --> 03:04:49,350
Tag!
-Oh!

443
03:04:49,360 --> 03:04:51,530
-Yay!

444
03:04:51,520 --> 03:04:52,850
-Oh, my God!

